    </p>
    <p>
        Since finishing school I have been working and learning about software engineering and I love.  I currently work at <a href = "//athenahealth.com">athenahealth</a> in Boston as a software developer, we are solving some really challenging problems related to healthcare technology.
    </p>
    <p>
         At Athena I started out working on interfaces between our software and other independent systems.  Working on interfaces I learned a lot about the challenges and requirements for successful data portability.  This year I started working on rebuilding how he handle clinical orders, it has been quite a challenge. 
    </p>

